OL,5, Staff at a local authority with the    
OL,6, highest sickness absence record in     
OL,7, Wales have been urged not to "beat     
OL,8, themselves up" about it.               
OL,10,FFigures show absences at Blaenau Gwent 
OL,11,Fcouncil rose in 2021/22 to almost 17   
OL,12,Fdays per full-time equivalent employee.
OL,14,FThe statistics were called "shocking"  
OL,15,Fby one councillor, Ross Leadbeater.    
OL,17,FBut one senior official said they could
OL,18,Freflect the high level of local health 
OL,19,Fproblems, and another councillor said  
OL,20,FCovid hit the area badly.              
